    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make your own shadow wrap around your body and make erratic movements, confusing your foes and granting you 15% concealment against melee attacks unless the attacker makes a save to keep focused enough to ignore the shadow. A successful save makes the attacker immune for a single round, after which it must save again when it attacks.<br><br>Blind creatures are immune to this technique.</p>\n\n\n\n",
